  "title": "Peppermint crisp-tert - soos van ouds - Marinda Kook",
  "description": null
 },
 "html": "<p>Daar is sekere kosse wat nooit uit die mode gaan nie.  Een daarvan is &#8216;n peppermintcrisp tert.  Ek het met dit groot geword en vandag nog is dit n gunsteling in ons huis.  Die lekkerte is dat dit as nagereg net so goed kan werk as  n tert vir teetyd. <a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/VARKSKOUER-010.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1882\" alt=\"VARKSKOUER 010\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/VARKSKOUER-010-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>BENODIG:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 tot 2 pakkies tennisbeskuitjies</li>\n<li>500 ml room</li>\n<li>1 blikkie caramel treat</li>\n<li>150 g peppermintcrisp sjokolade</li>\n<li>1 peppermint aero sjokolade<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-002.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1872\" alt=\"TERT 002\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-002-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOU:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>spuit n bak met spray and cook en pak die bodem toe met die tennisbeskuitjies<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-016.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1883\" alt=\"TERT 016\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-016-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>maak die karamel sag in n houer ( ek het sommer geroer met n vurk)<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-007.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1873\" alt=\"TERT 007\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-007-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>klits die room tot sagtepuntstadium<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-008.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1874\" alt=\"TERT 008\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-008-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>roer die karamel daarby</li>\n<li>breek die peppermintcrisp lekker fyn en meng dit by die roommengsel<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-015.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1877\" alt=\"TERT 015\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-015-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>skep van die roommengsel op die koekielaag</li>\n<li>pak weer n laag koekies en nog n roomlaag<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-017.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1878\" alt=\"TERT 017\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-017-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>krummel die aero heel bo-op<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-023.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1879\" alt=\"TERT 023\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/TERT-023-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>los in die yskas vir ten minste 2 uur om behoorlik te stol</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Hou niks terug as jy die tert eet nie. Vergeet een oomblik van n banting dieet.  Geniet elke oomblik.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/VARKSKOUER-007.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1880\" alt=\"VARKSKOUER 007\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/VARKSKOUER-007-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
